<h3 data-start="3293" data-end="3348">Q1. Is age relaxation applicable to all categories?</h3>
<p data-start="3349" data-end="3442">Yes, <strong data-start="3354" data-end="3413">all categories including General, OBC, SC, ST and women</strong> will get 3 years relaxation.</p>
<h3 data-start="3444" data-end="3485">Q2. Is this age relaxation permanent?</h3>
<p data-start="3486" data-end="3529">No, this is a <strong data-start="3500" data-end="3528">one-time relaxation only</strong>.</p>
