<p><span style="color: #ff0000;">Last Updated: 7 January 2026 | Next Update: Admit Card &amp; Exam Date</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #ff00ff;">Check RRB Group D Physical Test 2026 details. Know PET running time, weight lifting, height, chest &amp; medical standards.</span></p>
<h2 data-start="525" data-end="567">RRB Group D Physical Test 2026 СӮРҗРЈ Official Details</h2>
<p data-start="569" data-end="710"><strong data-start="569" data-end="603"><a href="https://www.uprojgar.com/rrb-group-d-vacancy-2026/">RRB Group D</a> Physical Test 2026</strong> СҖРҙв–‘СҖРөР—СҖРҙв–“СҖРҙв•ЎСҖРөР— СҖРҙРҪСҖРҙв–‘СҖРөРқСҖРҙРҙСҖРөРҗ СҖРҙРјСҖРөРӣСҖРҙв–‘СҖРөРқСҖРҙРұ СҖРҙР¶СҖРөРқСҖРҙв•ЎСҖРҙв•ӣСҖРҙв–‘СҖРҙв•ӣ СҖРҙР–СҖРҙРҝСҖРөРӣСҖРҙР¬СҖРҙв”җСҖРҙРҙ СҖРҙРҘСҖРҙв”җСҖРҙРҝСҖРҙв•ӣ СҖРҙР¬СҖРҙв•ӣСҖРҙРҙСҖРҙв•ӣ СҖРҙв•ЈСҖРөРҳСҖРөРҙ CBT СҖРҙРҫСҖРөР—СҖРҙР’ СҖРҙв••СҖРҙР»СҖРҙв–“ СҖРҙРҷСҖРҙРҫСҖРөРқСҖРҙРҫСҖРөРҗСҖРҙР¶СҖРҙв•ЎСҖРҙв•ӣСҖРҙв–‘СҖРөРӣСҖРҙР’ СҖРҙРҘСҖРөРӣ PET СҖРҙРӨСҖРҙв–‘ СҖРҙРҫСҖРөР—СҖРҙРұСҖРҙв”җСҖРҙРҘСҖРҙв–“ СҖРҙРҜСҖРөР—СҖРҙв••СҖРөРқСҖРҙРҜ СҖРҙР¶СҖРөР—СҖРҙРёСҖРҙв•ӣ СҖРҙв•ЈСҖРөРӣСҖРҙРҙСҖРҙв•ӣ СҖРҙв•ЈСҖРөРҳСҖРөРҙ</p>
<h2 data-start="717" data-end="753">Physical Efficiency Test (PET)</h2>
<h3 data-start="755" data-end="778">For Male Candidates</h3>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Test</th>
<th>Standard</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>Running</td>
<td>1000 meters in 4 min 15 sec</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Weight</td>
<td>Carry 35kg for 100 meters</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<h2></h2>
<h2>For Female Candidates</h2>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Test</th>
<th>Standard</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>Running</td>
<td>1000 meters in 5 min 40 sec</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Weight</td>
<td>Carry 20kg for 100 meters</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2>Height &amp; Chest Standard</h2>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Category</th>
<th>Height</th>
<th>Chest</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>Male</td>
<td>165 cm</td>
<td>80СӮРҗРЈ85 cm</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Female</td>
<td>157 cm</td>
<td>NA</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>(Relaxation for reserved category as per RRB rules)</p>
<h2 data-start="1257" data-end="1280">Medical Standards</h2>
<ul data-start="1282" data-end="1377">
<li data-start="1282" data-end="1296">
<p data-start="1284" data-end="1296">Eye vision</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1297" data-end="1316">
<p data-start="1299" data-end="1316">Hearing ability</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1317" data-end="1337">
<p data-start="1319" data-end="1337">No major disease</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1338" data-end="1377">
<p data-start="1340" data-end="1377">Fit as per Railway A-3/B-1 Standard</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 data-start="1384" data-end="1393">FAQs</h2>
<p data-start="1395" data-end="1425"><strong data-start="1395" data-end="1417">Q1. PET mandatory?</strong><br data-start="1417" data-end="1420" />Yes</p>
<p data-start="1427" data-end="1465"><strong data-start="1427" data-end="1458">Q2. CBT fail candidate PET?</strong><br data-start="1458" data-end="1461" />No</p>
<p data-start="2715" data-end="2764"><strong data-start="2719" data-end="2762">Q3. How many chances are given in PET?</strong></p>
<p data-start="2765" data-end="2843">Only <strong data-start="2770" data-end="2785">one attempt</strong> is allowed for PET. There is no re-test or second chance.</p>
<p data-start="2850" data-end="2906"><strong data-start="2854" data-end="2904">Q4. What documents should be carried for PET?</strong></p>
<p data-start="2907" data-end="2931">Candidates must carry:</p>
<ul data-start="2932" data-end="3045">
<li data-start="2932" data-end="2951">
<p data-start="2934" data-end="2951">PET call letter</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2952" data-end="2970">
<p data-start="2954" data-end="2970">Valid photo ID</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2971" data-end="3000">
<p data-start="2973" data-end="3000">Passport-size photographs</p>
</li>
<li data-start="3001" data-end="3045">
<p data-start="3003" data-end="3045">Medical/fitness certificates (if required)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="3052" data-end="3122"><strong data-start="3056" data-end="3120">Q5. Is PET conducted before or after document verification?</strong></p>
<p data-start="3123" data-end="3260">PET is usually conducted <strong data-start="3148" data-end="3186">before final document verification</strong>, but the exact sequence depends on the official schedule released by RRB.</p>
<p data-start="1427" data-end="1465">СҖРҙРҝСҖРҙв•Ј СҖРҙР¬СҖРҙв•ӣСҖРҙРёСҖРҙРҘСҖРҙв•ӣСҖРҙв–‘СҖРөРҗ <strong data-start="1634" data-end="1678"><a href="https://www.rrbapply.gov.in/#/auth/landing" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Railway Recruitment Board</a> PET Rules 2026</strong> СҖРҙРәСҖРҙв–‘ СҖРҙР–СҖРҙР·СҖРҙв•ӣСҖРҙв–‘СҖРҙв”җСҖРҙРҙ СҖРҙв•ЈСҖРөРҳСҖРөРҙ</p>
