<p data-start="220" data-end="612">The <strong data-start="224" data-end="257">University of Allahabad (UoA)</strong> has officially announced that all undergraduate (UG) admissions for the CUET UG 2026 Allahabad ,<strong data-start="330" data-end="358">academic session 2026СӮРҗРЈ27</strong> will be conducted through <strong data-start="385" data-end="435">CUET UG 2026 Allahabad University (Common University Entrance Test)</strong>. students seeking admission in <strong data-start="534" data-end="586">Allahabad University and its affiliated colleges</strong> must qualify for CUET UG.</p>
<p data-start="614" data-end="886">This decision has been taken in accordance with <strong data-start="662" data-end="710">UGC and the Ministry of Education guidelines</strong> and under the <strong data-start="725" data-end="765">National Education Policy (NEP) 2020</strong>. From this year onwards, <strong data-start="791" data-end="836">all UG courses will be four-year programs</strong>, and admissions will strictly follow CUET scores.</p>
<h2 data-start="893" data-end="957"><span style="font-size: 24pt;"><strong data-start="896" data-end="957">Important Dates for CUET UG 2026 Allahabad University</strong></span></h2>
